tools: sys.write,sys.download,github.com/nw0rn/text2speech-gptscript,github.com/dejwid/speech2text-gptscript
description: creates a text and images for a reel from a link
args: link: Link to the article
args: dir: Directory to save the files to

1. Go to ${dir} directory and find all files with filename like story-$INDEX.txt
2. For each file, read text inside the file and generate speech/voiceover for it  
3. Save to same dir with filename like speech-$INDEX
4. For saved speech/voiceover file, generate text/subtitles information
5. Save that info into same dir with filename subtitles-$INDEX